<p class="">is not the essential point whether the word"plot" covered the Schuman proposal? What other proposals were there before the public at the time, except the Schuman proposal we had just been debating? Surely the right hon. Gentleman will consider his own position very carefully in this matter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
